### Percent Change


::: {#fig-cum-change-belmac-percent .cell layout-ncol="2" hash='index_cache/html/fig-cum-change-belmac-percent_cc496c1e493438e4d0c1f7286137f79c'}
::: {.cell-output-display}
![Population](index_files/figure-html/fig-cum-change-belmac-percent-1.png){#fig-cum-change-belmac-percent-1 width=672}
:::

::: {.cell-output-display}
![Dwellings](index_files/figure-html/fig-cum-change-belmac-percent-2.png){#fig-cum-change-belmac-percent-2 width=672}
